trans-unit.source:
\n

Compares the value sent to the parameter, arguments, to the Arguments property of the current instance of DynamicExpression.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xxx xxxxx xxxx xx xxx xxxxxxxxx$ $xxxx$xxxxxxxxx$$xxxx$$ xx xxx $xxxxxx$Xxxxxxxxx$$xxxxxx$ xxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xx $xxxxxx$XxxxxxxXxxxxxxxxx$$xxxxxx$.

trans-unit.source: If the values of the parameter and the property are equal, the current instance is returned.
trans-unit.target: Xx xxx xxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxxxx xxx xxx xxxxxxxx xxx xxxxx$ xxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source: If they are not equal, a new DynamicExpression instance is returned that is identical to the current instance except that the Arguments property is set to the value of parameter arguments.
trans-unit.target: Xx xxxx xxx xxx xxxxx$ x xxx $xxxxxx$XxxxxxxXxxxxxxxxx$$xxxxxx$ xxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxx xxxx xx xxxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxxx xxx $xxxxxx$Xxxxxxxxx$$xxxxxx$ xxxxxxxx xx xxx xx xxx xxxxx xx xxxxxxxxx $xxxx$xxxxxxxxx$$xxxx$.
